<item>
            <title>[LU-9420] Bad Check slipped into repo</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9420</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5710&quot; title=&quot;correcting typos and grammar&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5710&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5710&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; landed, a check for message size was landed that should not have been. &#160;This check was part of a patch in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7650&quot; title=&quot;ko2iblnd map_on_demand can&amp;#39;t negotitate when page sizes are different between nodes.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7650&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7650&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which was later pulled because it broke things. &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5718&quot; title=&quot;RDMA too fragmented with router&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5718&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5718&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; picked up this code&#160;via its many rebases (it too forever to land &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5718&quot; title=&quot;RDMA too fragmented with router&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5718&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5718&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which is the core problem here).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket has been opened to remove this incorrect check. &#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
